    <h3 class="right_title">
      <div class="position">当前位置：<a href="/" title="首页">首页</a> &gt; <a href="/about/?2.html">潍博之信</a>&gt; <a href="/list/?3_1.html">规章制度</a></div>
      <span>规章制度</span> </h3>
    <div class="clear"></div>
    <div class="active" id="shownews">
      <h1 class="title">第六章 考古发掘</h1>
      <div class="editor"><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">第一条</span> &nbsp;</span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">根据《中华人民共和国文物保护法》</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">《考古发掘管理办法》等法律法规</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">，加强</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">本馆</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">考古发掘管理工作，保护</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">区域内</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">历史文化遗产</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">第二条</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">考古发掘管理</span></span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">本馆考古发掘管理工作以有利于区域内文物保护和配合区域经济发展为根本立足点，严格管理，科学发掘。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:47px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一、考古发掘人员</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:47px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">1、考古科为本馆考古发掘活动主体，其他科室考古学专业人员同时参加。</span></p><p style="text-indent:47px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">2、本馆其他科室非考古专业人员，因工作需要，经馆长批准，可参与、协助考古工作。</span></p><p style="text-indent:47px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">3、考古部门负责人及相关领导负责组织培训馆内考古团队、上报考古发掘申请报告、协调地方部门关系等，确保考古发掘工作顺利进行。</span></p><p style="text-indent:47px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">4、鼓励馆内考古专业人员申报获取考古工地负责人资格，鼓励馆内其他人员申报获取相应地考古资格。</span></p><p style="text-indent:47px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">5、馆内考古人员除需加强考古专业技术培训外，另须加强相关法律法规学习，确保考古发掘工作依法开展。</span></p><p style="text-indent:47px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">二、考古发掘财务</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1、考古科根据工作需要和年度计划，向财务科报请年度考古发掘预算，经馆长办公会议审核后，上报市财政年度预算。</span></p><p style="text-indent:47px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">2、为考古发掘配置相应的考古设备、车辆，按工作需要合理调度。</span></p><p style="text-indent:47px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">3、考古人员、技工等考古补贴按国家相关规定发放。</span></p><p style="text-indent:47px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">三、考古发掘工地</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:47px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">为保证考古工地</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">发掘</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">工作正常有序进行，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">确保文物安全，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">预防事故发生，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">须加强考古工地管理。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:47px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">1、安全管理</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>1）考古发掘工地现场管理坚持“人员安全，预防为主，安全第一；文物安全，保护为主，抢救第一”的原则。</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>2）</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">成立</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">考古</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">工地安全领导小组</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">、应急小组</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">，小组内成员分工明确，各司其职。考古</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">工地负责人为</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">第一安全责任人</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>3）</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">设立专人排查</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">工地</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">安全隐患，督导安全工作，并定期汇报</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">定期对考古队员和</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">工人</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">进行安全教育，加强考古工作者自身的安全保护意识。考古队员手机</span>24小时开机，随时应对突发事件</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>4）</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">在考古现场设置安全警示标志。原则上无成年人陪同的儿童不得进入工地；对进入工地的老人，要给予一定的照顾</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>5）</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">考古勘察现场工作间歇及夜间均设专人值班</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>6）</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">发生事故，必须严格查处。做到事故原因不明不放过、责任不清不放过、责任者未受到教育不放过、没有预防措施或措施不力不放过。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:47px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px">2、发掘管理</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>1）</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">考古发掘人员应严格</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">遵循</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">《田野考古工作规程》，严格执行考古发掘项目计划，确保发掘质量和文物安全</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>2）</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">在考古发掘工作中，考古发掘</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">人员应</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">事先</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">采取保护文物</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">安全的措施。对发掘中发现的重要遗物和遗迹，及时采取必要的保护措施</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>3）做好考古工地</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">遗迹</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">与文物</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">照片</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">、</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">绘图记录</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">、工作日记等记录，确保有据可查。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>4）考古发掘文物应及时入工地库房，设专人进行保护管理。</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>5）</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">考古</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">人员未经馆领导审核批准，不准</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">对社会公开发表</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">、传播发掘文物及相关资料。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>6）考古发掘结束后，考古团队</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">应及时将发掘经过、收获和经费使用情况，向</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">有关</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">部门提交书面报告，并尽快编</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">写</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">考古发掘报告</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">，</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">内容包括发掘经过、主要收获、经费的来源和使用情况、发掘现场及拟保留的遗迹现象处理</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p><br/></p><script src="/inc/AspCms_VisitsAdd.asp?id=479"></script></div>
      
